OL,6,FThe claim was made following expert
OL,7,Fevidence provided by leading Horizon
OL,8,Fengineer Gareth Jenkins in the trial
OL,9,Fof subpostmistress Seema Misra.
OL,11,FMr Williams told the probe he was
OL,12,F"truly sorry" for being associated
OL,13,Fwith the "greatest miscarriage of
OL,14,Fjustice we've seen".
OL,16,FMrs Misra, who began running a branch
OL,17,Fin West Byfleet, Surrey, in 2005, was
OL,18,Fhanded a 15-month prison sentence
OL,19,Fwhile eight weeks pregnant in November
OL,20,F2010 after being accused of stealing
OL,21,F#74,000.
