OL,6,FThe Post Office received advice from
OL,7,Fexternal barrister Simon Clarke in
OL,8,F2013 suggesting an expert witness, Mr
OL,9,FJenkins, and the Post Office had
OL,10,F"breached their duties" to the court,
OL,11,Fand subsequent advice suggested
OL,12,Fmeeting minutes talking about Horizon
OL,13,Fbugs had been shredded.
