OL,6,FQuestioned on his views on the
OL,7,Fwrongful conviction of Mrs Misra, Mr
OL,8,FWilliams told the inquiry: "I take no
OL,9,Fpride, comfort or confidence in having
OL,10,Fworked for an employer that has
OL,11,Fengaged in conducting the greatest
OL,12,Fmiscarriage of justice that we've
OL,13,Fseen, or however it has been described.
OL,15,F"I don't know where to go with this -
OL,16,Fit's awful that people with
OL,17,Fconvictions had them, and had them for
OL,18,Fthe length of time that they did.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/13
