OL,6,F"Those two things don't sit very
OL,7,Feasily together, do they?"
OL,9,FMr Williams replied: "No, they don't,
OL,10,Fsir. No, they don't."
OL,12,FMr Williams, who joined the company in
OL,13,F2012, was also pressed on what he knew
