OL,11,FAddressing the destruction of meeting
OL,12,Fminutes in advice given to the
OL,13,Forganisation, Mr Clarke had written:
OL,14,F"An instruction was then given that
OL,15,Fthose emails and minutes should be,
OL,16,Fand have been, destroyed: the word
OL,17,F'shredded' was conveyed to me."
