OL,6,FMr Williams said: "It's an extremely
OL,7,Fserious allegation."
OL,9,FMr Beer continued: "Presumably you
OL,10,Fwere quite shocked to read it?"
OL,12,FThe Post Office lawyer replied: "Yes."
OL,14,FMr Beer later asked: "What steps did
OL,15,Fyou take to ensure that it was
OL,16,Finvestigated in any way whatsoever?"
OL,18,FAfter the witness said he did not
OL,19,Frecall, the counsel to the inquiry
OL,20,Fcontinued: "Is the answer none?"
