OL,6,FMr Williams said: "I don't recall, the
OL,7,Fanswer is I don't recall."
OL,9,FMr Beer then said: "Do you think you
OL,10,Fought to have taken steps to ensure
OL,11,Fthat the allegations made in Mr
OL,12,FClarke's advice were investigated in
OL,13,Fany way whatsoever?"
OL,15,FMr Williams replied: "I can't remember
OL,16,Fwhat happened at that time 11 years
OL,17,Fago - so what I felt needed to be done
OL,18,For should be done I can't recall now."
